      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "RUBY JUAN (1) was prominent early from the tricky draw and did a fair job to be beaten 5 lengths into third (22.51) at this track in a Grade 3/4 over 388m. Has performed well from this box with a win and two minor placings to her name from three starts. Rates highly and will give a great sight. LAURIE'S RUPEE (3) boasts a consistent overall record including 13 wins from 56 starts, the latest winning (22.42) over 388m at this track. Solid record at the distance winning 11 races. Looks well placed here and has the ability. Go well. MIA ZIPPER (5) is worth forgiving last start after finishing seventh (25.82) at Maitland over 450m. The form from her last run stacks up well. Leading chance. AUSSIE OSCAR (2) profiles nicely here at this trip.",
